data.description: Welcome to 266 Brookfield Road.  This cozy 3 bed and 1 full bath sits on a corner lot in the heart of Avon Lake.  Updated kitchen with new flooring and a ton of cabinet space.   Off the kitchen is a fully updated 3 season room that leads to the attached 2 car garage with brand new garage door and storage shed.  The full bath includes a new bath/shower combo, huge vanity, large medicine cabinet and bathroom closet. This big corner lot with fenced in back and side yard is perfect for small children and pets. Brand new hot water tank, new high efficiency furnace and central air in 2022. This home is move in ready, in the highly rated school system.  Beach and city pool access within a short distance. Minutes to I90 via Rt 83.  Make your appointment today to view this must see property.
